{
  "video_id": "SF242mxtZN8",
  "title": "Sonia Shah: 3 reasons we still haven't gotten rid of malaria",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12822.0,
      "end_time": 16257.0,
      "text": "So over the long course of human history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16257.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18749.0,
      "text": "the infectious disease that&#39;s killed more humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18749.0,
      "end_time": 21235.0,
      "text": "than any other is malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21235.0,
      "end_time": 24096.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s carried in the bites of infected mosquitos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24096.0,
      "end_time": 26305.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s probably our oldest scourge."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26305.0,
      "end_time": 30192.0,
      "text": "We may have had malaria since we evolved from the apes."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30192.0,
      "end_time": 33794.0,
      "text": "And to this day, malaria takes a huge toll on our species."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33794.0,
      "end_time": 36245.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got 300 million cases a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36245.0,
      "end_time": 39237.0,
      "text": "and over half a million deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39237.0,
      "end_time": 42202.0,
      "text": "Now this really makes no sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42202.0,
      "end_time": 44854.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve known how to cure malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44854.0,
      "end_time": 46494.0,
      "text": "since the 1600s."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46494.0,
      "end_time": 48791.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when Jesuit missionaries in Peru"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48791.0,
      "end_time": 51693.0,
      "text": "discovered the bark of the cinchona tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51693.0,
      "end_time": 53566.0,
      "text": "and inside that bark was quinine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53566.0,
      "end_time": 56904.0,
      "text": "still an effective cure for malaria to this day."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56904.0,
      "end_time": 59805.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve known how to cure malaria for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59805.0,
      "end_time": 62989.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve known how to prevent malaria since 1897."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62989.0,
      "end_time": 65262.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when the British army surgeon Ronald Ross"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65262.0,
      "end_time": 68620.0,
      "text": "discovered that it was mosquitos that carried malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68620.0,
      "end_time": 72812.0,
      "text": "not bad air or miasmas, as was previously thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72812.0,
      "end_time": 78095.0,
      "text": "So malaria should be a relatively simple disease to solve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78095.0,
      "end_time": 82025.0,
      "text": "and yet to this day, hundreds of thousands of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82025.0,
      "end_time": 85500.0,
      "text": "are going to die from the bite of a mosquito."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85500.0,
      "end_time": 86745.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86745.0,
      "end_time": 88275.0,
      "text": "This is a question that&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88275.0,
      "end_time": 90430.0,
      "text": "personally intrigued me for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90430.0,
      "end_time": 93189.0,
      "text": "I grew up as the daughter of Indian immigrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93189.0,
      "end_time": 95448.0,
      "text": "visiting my cousins in India every summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95448.0,
      "end_time": 98636.0,
      "text": "and because I had no immunity to the local malarias,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98636.0,
      "end_time": 102870.0,
      "text": "I was made to sleep under this hot, sweaty mosquito net every night"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102870.0,
      "end_time": 104561.0,
      "text": "while my cousins, they were allowed to sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104561.0,
      "end_time": 105790.0,
      "text": "out on the terrace and have"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105790.0,
      "end_time": 108552.0,
      "text": "this nice, cool night breeze wafting over them."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108552.0,
      "end_time": 112076.0,
      "text": "And I really hated the mosquitos for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112076.0,
      "end_time": 115444.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, I come from a Jain family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115444.0,
      "end_time": 117758.0,
      "text": "and Jainism is a religion that espouses"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117758.0,
      "end_time": 120896.0,
      "text": "a very extreme form of nonviolence."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120896.0,
      "end_time": 124224.0,
      "text": "So Jains are not supposed to eat meat."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124224.0,
      "end_time": 126081.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not supposed to walk on grass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126081.0,
      "end_time": 127342.0,
      "text": "because you could, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127342.0,
      "end_time": 129242.0,
      "text": "inadvertently kill some insects when you walk on grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129241.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132019.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re certainly not supposed to swat mosquitos."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132019.0,
      "end_time": 135735.0,
      "text": "So the fearsome power of this little insect"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135735.0,
      "end_time": 137714.0,
      "text": "was apparent to me from a very young age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137714.0,
      "end_time": 140985.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s one reason why I spent five years as a journalist"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140985.0,
      "end_time": 143673.0,
      "text": "trying to understand, why has malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143673.0,
      "end_time": 148213.0,
      "text": "been such a horrible scourge for all of us for so very long?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148213.0,
      "end_time": 150870.0,
      "text": "And I think there&#39;s three main reasons why."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150870.0,
      "end_time": 153338.0,
      "text": "Those three reasons add up to the fourth reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153338.0,
      "end_time": 156149.0,
      "text": "which is probably the biggest reason of all."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156149.0,
      "end_time": 159110.0,
      "text": "The first reason is certainly scientific."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159110.0,
      "end_time": 161425.0,
      "text": "This little parasite that causes malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161425.0,
      "end_time": 163352.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s probably one of the most complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163352.0,
      "end_time": 165943.0,
      "text": "and wily pathogens known to humankind."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165943.0,
      "end_time": 169283.0,
      "text": "It lives half its life inside the cold-blooded mosquito"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169283.0,
      "end_time": 173685.0,
      "text": "and half its life inside the warm-blooded human."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173685.0,
      "end_time": 176683.0,
      "text": "These two environments are totally different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176683.0,
      "end_time": 179699.0,
      "text": "but not only that, they&#39;re both utterly hostile."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179699.0,
      "end_time": 183706.0,
      "text": "So the insect is continually trying to fight off the parasite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183706.0,
      "end_time": 186667.0,
      "text": "and so is the human body continually trying to fight it off."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186667.0,
      "end_time": 190417.0,
      "text": "This little creature survives under siege like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190417.0,
      "end_time": 193492.0,
      "text": "but not only does it survive, it has thrived."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193492.0,
      "end_time": 197814.0,
      "text": "It has spread. It has more ways to evade attack than we know."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197814.0,
      "end_time": 199928.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a shape-shifter, for one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199928.0,
      "end_time": 203087.0,
      "text": "Just as a caterpillar turns into a butterfly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203087.0,
      "end_time": 205726.0,
      "text": "the malaria parasite transforms itself like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205726.0,
      "end_time": 208949.0,
      "text": "seven times in its life cycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208949.0,
      "end_time": 213206.0,
      "text": "And each of those life stages not only looks totally different from each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213206.0,
      "end_time": 216270.0,
      "text": "they have totally different physiology."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216270.0,
      "end_time": 218262.0,
      "text": "So say you came up with some great drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 218262.0,
      "end_time": 221202.0,
      "text": "that worked against one stage of the parasite&#39;s life cycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221202.0,
      "end_time": 224667.0,
      "text": "It might do nothing at all to any of the other stages."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224667.0,
      "end_time": 227530.0,
      "text": "It can hide in our bodies, undetected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227530.0,
      "end_time": 229894.0,
      "text": "unbeknownst to us, for days, for weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229894.0,
      "end_time": 233693.0,
      "text": "for months, for years, in some cases even decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 233693.0,
      "end_time": 238077.0,
      "text": "So the parasite is a very big scientific challenge to tackle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238077.0,
      "end_time": 241282.0,
      "text": "but so is the mosquito that carries the parasite."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241282.0,
      "end_time": 243580.0,
      "text": "Only about 12 species of mosquitos"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 243580.0,
      "end_time": 245514.0,
      "text": "carry most of the world&#39;s malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245514.0,
      "end_time": 247990.0,
      "text": "and we know quite a bit about the kinds of"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247990.0,
      "end_time": 250915.0,
      "text": "watery habitats that they specialize in."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 250915.0,
      "end_time": 253197.0,
      "text": "So you might think, then, well, why don&#39;t we just"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 253197.0,
      "end_time": 256353.0,
      "text": "avoid the places where the killer mosquitos live? Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256353.0,
      "end_time": 258631.0,
      "text": "We could avoid the places where the killer grizzly bears live"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258630.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261389.99999999997,
      "text": "and we avoid the places where the killer crocodiles live."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 261390.0,
      "end_time": 264620.0,
      "text": "But say you live in the tropics"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 264620.0,
      "end_time": 267893.0,
      "text": "and you walk outside your hut one day"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 267893.0,
      "end_time": 269915.0,
      "text": "and you leave some footprints in the soft dirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 269915.0,
      "end_time": 271838.0,
      "text": "around your home."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 271838.0,
      "end_time": 275068.0,
      "text": "Or say your cow does, or say your pig does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275068.0,
      "end_time": 277202.0,
      "text": "and then, say, it rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 277202.0,
      "end_time": 279570.0,
      "text": "and that footprint fills up with a little bit of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 279570.0,
      "end_time": 281651.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it. You&#39;ve created the perfect"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 281651.0,
      "end_time": 285229.0,
      "text": "malarial mosquito habitat that&#39;s right outside your door."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 285229.0,
      "end_time": 288091.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not easy for us to extricate ourselves from these insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288091.0,
      "end_time": 290725.0,
      "text": "We kind of create places that they love to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290725.0,
      "end_time": 292724.0,
      "text": "just by living our own lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 292724.0,
      "end_time": 294103.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a huge scientific challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 294103.0,
      "end_time": 296310.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a huge economic challenge too."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296310.0,
      "end_time": 298245.0,
      "text": "Malaria occurs in some of the poorest"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 298245.0,
      "end_time": 300184.0,
      "text": "and most remote places on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 300184.0,
      "end_time": 302029.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s a reason for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 302029.0,
      "end_time": 304729.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re poor, you&#39;re more likely to get malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 304729.0,
      "end_time": 306882.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re poor, you&#39;re more likely to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 306882.0,
      "end_time": 310951.0,
      "text": "in rudimentary housing on marginal land that&#39;s poorly drained."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 310951.0,
      "end_time": 313540.0,
      "text": "These are places where mosquitos breed."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 313540.0,
      "end_time": 317140.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re less likely to have door screens or window screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 317140.0,
      "end_time": 319043.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re less likely to have electricity"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 319043.0,
      "end_time": 322049.0,
      "text": "and all the indoor activities that electricity makes possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 322049.0,
      "end_time": 323282.0,
      "text": "so you&#39;re outside more."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 323282.0,
      "end_time": 325614.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re getting bitten by mosquitos more."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 325614.0,
      "end_time": 327239.0,
      "text": "So poverty causes malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 327239.0,
      "end_time": 330272.0,
      "text": "but what we also know now is that malaria itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 330272.0,
      "end_time": 331919.0,
      "text": "causes poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 331919.0,
      "end_time": 334570.0,
      "text": "For one thing, it strikes hardest during harvest season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 334570.0,
      "end_time": 337326.0,
      "text": "so exactly when farmers need to be out in the fields"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 337326.0,
      "end_time": 341235.0,
      "text": "collecting their crops, they&#39;re home sick with a fever."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 341235.0,
      "end_time": 344096.0,
      "text": "But it also predisposes people to death"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344096.0,
      "end_time": 345881.0,
      "text": "from all other causes."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 345881.0,
      "end_time": 347241.0,
      "text": "So this has happened historically."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 347241.0,
      "end_time": 350623.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been able to take malaria out of a society."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 350623.0,
      "end_time": 352080.0,
      "text": "Everything else stays the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 352080.0,
      "end_time": 354755.0,
      "text": "so we still have bad food, bad water, bad sanitation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 354755.0,
      "end_time": 356516.0,
      "text": "all the things that make people sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 356516.0,
      "end_time": 358660.0,
      "text": "But just if you take malaria out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 358660.0,
      "end_time": 362472.0,
      "text": "deaths from everything else go down."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 362472.0,
      "end_time": 365183.0,
      "text": "And the economist Jeff Sachs has actually quantified"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 365183.0,
      "end_time": 367368.0,
      "text": "what this means for a society."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 367368.0,
      "end_time": 370122.0,
      "text": "What it means is, if you have malaria in your society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 370122.0,
      "end_time": 372583.0,
      "text": "your economic growth is depressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 372583.0,
      "end_time": 376553.0,
      "text": "by 1.3 percent every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 376553.0,
      "end_time": 380352.0,
      "text": "year after year after year, just this one disease alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 380352.0,
      "end_time": 382916.0,
      "text": "So this poses a huge economic challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 382916.0,
      "end_time": 385100.0,
      "text": "because say you do come up with your great drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 385100.0,
      "end_time": 387310.0,
      "text": "or your great vaccine -- how do you deliver it"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 387310.0,
      "end_time": 389880.0,
      "text": "in a place where there&#39;s no roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 389880.0,
      "end_time": 391073.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 391073.0,
      "end_time": 394407.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no electricity for refrigeration to keep things cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 394407.0,
      "end_time": 397127.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no clinics, there&#39;s no clinicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 397127.0,
      "end_time": 399661.0,
      "text": "to deliver these things where they&#39;re needed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 399661.0,
      "end_time": 403664.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a huge economic challenge in taming malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 403664.0,
      "end_time": 406720.0,
      "text": "But along with the scientific challenge and the economic challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 406720.0,
      "end_time": 408532.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s also a cultural challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 408532.0,
      "end_time": 411917.0,
      "text": "and this is probably the part about malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 411917.0,
      "end_time": 414218.0,
      "text": "that people don&#39;t like to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 414218.0,
      "end_time": 416929.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the paradox that the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 416929.0,
      "end_time": 418737.0,
      "text": "who have the most malaria in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 418737.0,
      "end_time": 421317.0,
      "text": "tend to care about it the least."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 421317.0,
      "end_time": 424729.0,
      "text": "This has been the finding of medical anthropologists again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 424729.0,
      "end_time": 427496.0,
      "text": "They ask people in malarious parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 427496.0,
      "end_time": 429552.0,
      "text": "&quot;What do you think about malaria?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 429552.0,
      "end_time": 433461.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t say, &quot;It&#39;s a killer disease. We&#39;re scared of it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 433461.0,
      "end_time": 438799.0,
      "text": "They say, &quot;Malaria is a normal problem of life.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 438799.0,
      "end_time": 440565.0,
      "text": "And that was certainly my personal experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 440565.0,
      "end_time": 442584.0,
      "text": "When I told my relatives in India"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 442584.0,
      "end_time": 444068.0,
      "text": "that I was writing a book about malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 444068.0,
      "end_time": 446035.0,
      "text": "they kind of looked at me like"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 446035.0,
      "end_time": 448736.0,
      "text": "I told them I was writing a book about warts or something."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 448736.0,
      "end_time": 451783.0,
      "text": "Like, why would you write about something so boring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 451783.0,
      "end_time": 453449.0,
      "text": "so ordinary? You know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 453449.0,
      "end_time": 456177.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s simple risk perception, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 456177.0,
      "end_time": 458612.0,
      "text": "A child in Malawi, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 458612.0,
      "end_time": 463424.0,
      "text": "she might have 12 episodes of malaria before the age of two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 463424.0,
      "end_time": 465477.0,
      "text": "but if she survives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 465477.0,
      "end_time": 468091.0,
      "text": "she&#39;ll continue to get malaria throughout her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 468091.0,
      "end_time": 470814.0,
      "text": "but she&#39;s much less likely to die of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 470814.0,
      "end_time": 472766.0,
      "text": "And so in her lived experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 472766.0,
      "end_time": 476097.0,
      "text": "malaria is something that comes and goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 476097.0,
      "end_time": 478127.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s actually true for most of the world&#39;s malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 478127.0,
      "end_time": 481704.0,
      "text": "Most of the world&#39;s malaria comes and goes on its own."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 481704.0,
      "end_time": 484828.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just, there&#39;s so much malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 484828.0,
      "end_time": 488599.0,
      "text": "that this tiny fraction of cases that end in death"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 488599.0,
      "end_time": 491560.0,
      "text": "add up to this big, huge number."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 491560.0,
      "end_time": 493553.0,
      "text": "So I think people in malarious parts of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 493553.0,
      "end_time": 495075.0,
      "text": "must think of malaria the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 495075.0,
      "end_time": 496734.0,
      "text": "those of us who live in the temperate world"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 496734.0,
      "end_time": 498985.0,
      "text": "think of cold and flu. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 498985.0,
      "end_time": 502391.0,
      "text": "Cold and flu have a huge burden on our societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 502391.0,
      "end_time": 504072.0,
      "text": "and on our own lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 504072.0,
      "end_time": 505336.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t really even take"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 505336.0,
      "end_time": 507878.0,
      "text": "the most rudimentary precautions against it because"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 507878.0,
      "end_time": 510599.0,
      "text": "we consider it normal to get cold and flu"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 510599.0,
      "end_time": 512836.0,
      "text": "during cold and flu season."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 512836.0,
      "end_time": 517248.0,
      "text": "And so this poses a huge cultural challenge in taming malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 517248.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521022.00000000006,
      "text": "because if people think it&#39;s normal to have malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 521022.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524480.0,
      "text": "then how do you get them to run to the doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 524480.0,
      "end_time": 527626.0,
      "text": "to get diagnosed, to pick up their prescription,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 527626.0,
      "end_time": 529148.0,
      "text": "to get it filled, to take the drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 529148.0,
      "end_time": 532627.0,
      "text": "to put on the repellents, to tuck in the bed nets?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 532627.0,
      "end_time": 537294.0,
      "text": "This is a huge cultural challenge in taming this disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 537294.0,
      "end_time": 538796.0,
      "text": "So take all that together."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 538796.0,
      "end_time": 543248.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got a disease. It&#39;s scientifically complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 543248.0,
      "end_time": 545676.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s economically challenging to deal with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 545676.0,
      "end_time": 547321.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s one for which the people who stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 547321.0,
      "end_time": 549625.0,
      "text": "to benefit the most care about it the least."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 549625.0,
      "end_time": 551713.0,
      "text": "And that adds up to the biggest problem of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 551713.0,
      "end_time": 554662.0,
      "text": "which, of course, is the political problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 554662.0,
      "end_time": 557520.0,
      "text": "How do you get a political leader to do anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 557520.0,
      "end_time": 559581.0,
      "text": "about a problem like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 559581.0,
      "end_time": 564206.0,
      "text": "And the answer is, historically, you don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 564206.0,
      "end_time": 566339.0,
      "text": "Most malarious societies throughout history"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 566339.0,
      "end_time": 568455.0,
      "text": "have simply lived with the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 568455.0,
      "end_time": 570458.0,
      "text": "So the main attacks on malaria have come"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 570458.0,
      "end_time": 573082.0,
      "text": "from outside of malarious societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 573082.0,
      "end_time": 574876.0,
      "text": "from people who aren&#39;t constrained"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 574876.0,
      "end_time": 577855.0,
      "text": "by these rather paralyzing politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 577855.0,
      "end_time": 581150.0,
      "text": "But this, I think, introduces a whole host of other kinds of difficulties."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 581150.0,
      "end_time": 583570.0,
      "text": "The first concerted attack against malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 583570.0,
      "end_time": 585316.0,
      "text": "started in the 1950s."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 585316.0,
      "end_time": 588406.0,
      "text": "It was the brainchild of the U.S. State Department."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 588406.0,
      "end_time": 591443.0,
      "text": "And this effort well understood the economic challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 591443.0,
      "end_time": 594924.0,
      "text": "They knew they had to focus on cheap, easy-to-use tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 594924.0,
      "end_time": 596699.0,
      "text": "and they focused on DDT."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 596699.0,
      "end_time": 598138.0,
      "text": "They understood the cultural challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 598138.0,
      "end_time": 601143.0,
      "text": "In fact, their rather patronizing view was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 601143.0,
      "end_time": 604046.0,
      "text": "people at risk of malaria shouldn&#39;t be asked to do anything at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 604046.0,
      "end_time": 607768.0,
      "text": "Everything should be done to them and for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 607768.0,
      "end_time": 610888.0,
      "text": "But they greatly underestimated the scientific challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 610888.0,
      "end_time": 613215.0,
      "text": "They had so much faith in their tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 613215.0,
      "end_time": 616206.0,
      "text": "that they stopped doing malaria research."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 616206.0,
      "end_time": 618674.0,
      "text": "And so when those tools started to fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 618674.0,
      "end_time": 621374.0,
      "text": "and public opinion started to turn against those tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 621374.0,
      "end_time": 625568.0,
      "text": "they had no scientific expertise to figure out what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 625568.0,
      "end_time": 629019.0,
      "text": "The whole campaign crashed, malaria resurged back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 629019.0,
      "end_time": 630833.0,
      "text": "but now it was even worse than before"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 630833.0,
      "end_time": 633594.0,
      "text": "because it was corralled into the hardest-to-reach places"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 633594.0,
      "end_time": 636780.0,
      "text": "in the most difficult-to-control forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 636780.0,
      "end_time": 640079.0,
      "text": "One WHO official at the time actually called that whole campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 640079.0,
      "end_time": 645136.0,
      "text": "&quot;one of the greatest mistakes ever made in public health.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 645136.0,
      "end_time": 647643.0,
      "text": "The latest effort to tame malaria started in the late 1990s."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 647643.0,
      "end_time": 651355.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s similarly directed and financed primarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 651355.0,
      "end_time": 653503.0,
      "text": "from outside of malarious societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 653503.0,
      "end_time": 656007.0,
      "text": "Now this effort well understands the scientific challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 656007.0,
      "end_time": 658228.0,
      "text": "They are doing tons of malaria research."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 658228.0,
      "end_time": 660681.0,
      "text": "And they understand the economic challenge too."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 660681.0,
      "end_time": 664241.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re focusing on very cheap, very easy-to-use tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 664241.0,
      "end_time": 668133.0,
      "text": "But now, I think, the dilemma is the cultural challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 668133.0,
      "end_time": 671767.0,
      "text": "The centerpiece of the current effort is the bed net."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 671767.0,
      "end_time": 673543.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s treated with insecticides."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 673543.0,
      "end_time": 675913.0,
      "text": "This thing has been distributed across the malarious world"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 675913.0,
      "end_time": 677346.0,
      "text": "by the millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 677346.0,
      "end_time": 679578.0,
      "text": "And when you think about the bed net,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 679578.0,
      "end_time": 682137.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s sort of a surgical intervention."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 682137.0,
      "end_time": 684283.0,
      "text": "You know, it doesn&#39;t really have any value"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 684283.0,
      "end_time": 687946.0,
      "text": "to a family with malaria except that it helps prevent malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 687946.0,
      "end_time": 691955.0,
      "text": "And yet we&#39;re asking people to use these nets every night."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 691955.0,
      "end_time": 693232.0,
      "text": "They have to sleep under them every night."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 693232.0,
      "end_time": 695269.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the only way they are effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 695269.0,
      "end_time": 696622.0,
      "text": "And they have to do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 696622.0,
      "end_time": 699708.0,
      "text": "even if the net blocks the breeze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 699708.0,
      "end_time": 702853.0,
      "text": "even if they might have to get up in the middle of the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 702853.0,
      "end_time": 704387.0,
      "text": "and relieve themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 704387.0,
      "end_time": 706636.0,
      "text": "even if they might have to move all their furnishings"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 706636.0,
      "end_time": 708103.0,
      "text": "to put this thing up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 708103.0,
      "end_time": 710956.0,
      "text": "even if, you know, they might live in a round hut"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 710956.0,
      "end_time": 714693.0,
      "text": "in which it&#39;s difficult to string up a square net."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 714693.0,
      "end_time": 719631.0,
      "text": "Now that&#39;s no big deal if you&#39;re fighting a killer disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 719631.0,
      "end_time": 721962.0,
      "text": "I mean, these are minor inconveniences."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 721962.0,
      "end_time": 725801.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not how people with malaria think of malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 725801.0,
      "end_time": 730681.0,
      "text": "So for them, the calculus must be quite different."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 730681.0,
      "end_time": 734599.0,
      "text": "Imagine, for example, if a bunch of well-meaning Kenyans"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 734599.0,
      "end_time": 736680.0,
      "text": "came up to those of us in the temperate world and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 736680.0,
      "end_time": 739502.0,
      "text": "&quot;You know, you people have a lot of cold and flu."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 739502.0,
      "end_time": 742630.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve designed this great, easy-to-use, cheap tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 742630.0,
      "end_time": 743700.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to give it to you for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 743700.0,
      "end_time": 745133.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called a face mask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 745133.0,
      "end_time": 749006.0,
      "text": "and all you need to do is"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 749006.0,
      "end_time": 751416.0,
      "text": "wear it every day during cold and flu season"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 751416.0,
      "end_time": 754185.0,
      "text": "when you go to school and when you go to work.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 754185.0,
      "end_time": 756115.0,
      "text": "Would we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 756115.0,
      "end_time": 758251.0,
      "text": "And I wonder if that&#39;s how people"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 758251.0,
      "end_time": 760317.0,
      "text": "in the malarious world thought of those nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 760317.0,
      "end_time": 762020.0,
      "text": "when they first received them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 762020.0,
      "end_time": 765418.0,
      "text": "Indeed, we know from studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 765418.0,
      "end_time": 768096.0,
      "text": "that only 20 percent of the bed nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 768096.0,
      "end_time": 771264.0,
      "text": "that were first distributed were actually used."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 771264.0,
      "end_time": 772975.0,
      "text": "And even that&#39;s probably an overestimate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 772975.0,
      "end_time": 775397.0,
      "text": "because the same people who distributed the nets"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 775397.0,
      "end_time": 776888.0,
      "text": "went back and asked the recipients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 776888.0,
      "end_time": 779361.0,
      "text": "&quot;Oh, did you use that net I gave you?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 779361.0,
      "end_time": 781973.0,
      "text": "Which is like your Aunt Jane asking you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 781973.0,
      "end_time": 784934.0,
      "text": "&quot;Oh, did you use that vase I gave you for Christmas?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 784934.0,
      "end_time": 786800.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s probably an overestimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 786800.0,
      "end_time": 790124.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not an insurmountable problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 790124.0,
      "end_time": 791954.0,
      "text": "We can do more education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 791954.0,
      "end_time": 794629.0,
      "text": "we can try to convince these people to use the nets."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 794629.0,
      "end_time": 795904.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what happening now."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 795904.0,
      "end_time": 797608.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re throwing a lot more time and money"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 797608.0,
      "end_time": 802125.0,
      "text": "into workshops and trainings and musicals and plays"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 802125.0,
      "end_time": 804538.0,
      "text": "and school meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 804538.0,
      "end_time": 806833.0,
      "text": "all these things to convince people"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 806833.0,
      "end_time": 809317.0,
      "text": "to use the nets we gave you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 809317.0,
      "end_time": 811457.0,
      "text": "And that might work."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 811457.0,
      "end_time": 814135.0,
      "text": "But it takes time. It takes money."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 814135.0,
      "end_time": 816915.0,
      "text": "It takes resources. It takes infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 816915.0,
      "end_time": 819597.0,
      "text": "It takes all the things that that cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 819597.0,
      "end_time": 822376.0,
      "text": "easy-to-use bed net was not supposed to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 822376.0,
      "end_time": 825780.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s difficult to attack malaria from inside malarious societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 825780.0,
      "end_time": 828318.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s equally tricky when we try to attack it"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 828318.0,
      "end_time": 831128.0,
      "text": "from outside of those societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 831128.0,
      "end_time": 832915.0,
      "text": "We end up imposing our own priorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 832915.0,
      "end_time": 834459.0,
      "text": "on the people of the malarious world."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 834459.0,
      "end_time": 837253.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s exactly what we did in the 1950s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 837253.0,
      "end_time": 839131.0,
      "text": "and that effort backfired."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 839131.0,
      "end_time": 840762.0,
      "text": "I would argue today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 840762.0,
      "end_time": 844992.0,
      "text": "when we are distributing tools that we&#39;ve designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 844992.0,
      "end_time": 848745.0,
      "text": "and that don&#39;t necessarily make sense in people&#39;s lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 848745.0,
      "end_time": 852298.0,
      "text": "we run the risk of making the same mistake again."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 852298.0,
      "end_time": 854106.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not to say that malaria is unconquerable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 854106.0,
      "end_time": 855569.0,
      "text": "because I think it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 855569.0,
      "end_time": 857777.0,
      "text": "but what if we attacked this disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 857777.0,
      "end_time": 861320.0,
      "text": "according to the priorities of the people who lived with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 861320.0,
      "end_time": 863756.0,
      "text": "Take the example of England and the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 863756.0,
      "end_time": 866927.0,
      "text": "We had malaria in those countries for hundreds of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 866927.0,
      "end_time": 869085.0,
      "text": "and we got rid of it completely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 869085.0,
      "end_time": 872094.0,
      "text": "not because we attacked malaria. We didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 872094.0,
      "end_time": 876201.0,
      "text": "We attacked bad roads and bad houses"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 876201.0,
      "end_time": 881083.0,
      "text": "and bad drainage and lack of electricity and rural poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 881083.0,
      "end_time": 884400.0,
      "text": "We attacked the malarious way of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 884400.0,
      "end_time": 890120.0,
      "text": "and by doing that, we slowly built malaria out."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 890120.0,
      "end_time": 891758.0,
      "text": "Now attacking the malarious way of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 891758.0,
      "end_time": 895320.0,
      "text": "this is something -- these are things people care about today."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 895320.0,
      "end_time": 897707.0,
      "text": "And attacking the malarious way of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 897707.0,
      "end_time": 902466.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not fast, it&#39;s not cheap, it&#39;s not easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 902466.0,
      "end_time": 905534.0,
      "text": "but I think it&#39;s the only lasting way forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 905534.0,
      "end_time": 906827.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 906827.0,
      "end_time": 916827.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}